      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Nov 2024 01:04:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普引发的比特币上涨对韩国小型股来说是个坏消息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-27/bitcoin-s-trump-inspired-rally-is-bad-news-for-korean-small-caps</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 最近赢得大选以来，比特币的迅猛上涨给资本市场的一隅带来了巨大压力：韩国的小型股。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-27/bitcoin-s-trump-inspired-rally-is-bad-news-for-korean-small-caps</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 22:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>比特币恢复上涨，重燃 10 万美元里程碑乐观情绪</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-27/bitcoin-btc-bounces-off-lows-rekindles-100-000-milestone-optimism</link>
      <description><![CDATA[比特币再次回升至难以捉摸的 10 万美元价格水平，结束了自唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 的总统胜利引发最大加密货币创纪录上涨以来最长的下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-27/bitcoin-btc-bounces-off-lows-rekindles-100-000-milestone-optimism</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 16:13:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Tether 支持的 Northern Data 收到加密货币挖矿部门的收购要约</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-27/tether-backed-northern-data-gets-offers-for-crypto-mining-arm</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Northern Data AG 希望利用 11 月份比特币的涨势获利，该公司即将达成出售其加密货币挖矿业务的协议。]]></description>
